      "body": "Commander {username},\n\nYou awake in the command chamber of {colony_name}. The colony AI confirms a stable economy, an initial fleet, and enough supplies to secure your first expansion corridor.\n\nA forgotten relay beacon in the outer orbit is transmitting fragmented star charts and references to ancient precursor ruins. Your task is clear: stabilize your sector, scout nearby systems, and decide what kind of empire this world will become.\n\nThe galaxy is young again. Write its next chapter."
